    <mj-section padding="20px 20px 0 20px" background-color="#00B9FF">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#fff" font-weight="400" padding="30px 40px 10px 40px" font-size="30px" line-height="40px" color="#32325d">Welcome back! </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
   
    <mj-section padding="0 20px 20px 20px" background-color="#00B9FF">
      <mj-column width="80%">
        <mj-text align="center" line-height="28px" color="#fff" font-size="19px" color="#424770" padding-top="10px" padding-bottom="40px" font-weight="300" padding="0px">Many have been away for summer vacations (and we hope everyone have had a great time!). During the summer we have been hard at work, so this newletter is packed with updates. We have everything from case studies to new concepts and a fresh website! </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    
    <mj-section background-color="#f6f9fc">
      <mj-column  width="100%">
        <mj-image src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/aidhedge-newsletter/lineshadow-4.png" alt="" align="center" border="none" padding="0px"></mj-image>
</mj-column>
 </mj-section>

         <mj-section background-color="#f6f9fc" >
      <mj-column>
        
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>


  <mj-section background-color="#f6f9fc">
 <mj-group>
  <mj-column css-class="hide-on-mobile">
        <mj-image  padding="30px 30px 0px 25px"src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/aidhedge-newsletter/complex-project.png" alt="" align="center" border="none" padding="0px"></mj-image>
</mj-column>
      <mj-column css-class="full-on-mobile">
      <mj-text css-class="aligned-center" align="center" font-weight="500" padding="30px 20px 0px 25px" font-size="20px" line-height="20px" text-transform="uppercase" color="#32325d">Cases</mj-text>
        <mj-text css-class="aligned-center" color="#525f7f" align="center"  
        font-weight="300">During the last year we have been working hard with our partners, trying out ways to improve how the do transactions and financial management. Allways with the aim om getting more and better funding to projects and recipients. Check out a few examples, <a href="https://story.aidhedge.org/world-vision-case-currency-risk-in-a-multi-partner-and-multi-country-project-6478aa275642">covering budget and risk in complex projects</a>, <a href="https://story.aidhedge.org/more-funding-with-better-fx-transactions-the-case-of-social-initiative-f149655aef2d">better transactions</a> and <a href="https://story.aidhedge.org/case-predictable-funding-to-india-5efeda855fe7">predictable funding</a>.</mj-text>
</mj-column>
 </mj-group>


</mj-section>
