  <mj-section background-color="#f6f9fc">
   <mj-group>
  <mj-column css-class="hide-on-mobile" >
<mj-image padding="10px 30px 0px 25px"src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/aidhedge-newsletter/www.aidhedge.org_concepts.png" alt="" align="center" border="none" padding="0px"></mj-image>
</mj-column>
      <mj-column css-class="full-on-mobile">
      <mj-text css-class="aligned-center" align="center" font-weight="500" padding="10px 20px 10px 10px"  font-size="20px" line-height="20px" text-transform="uppercase" color="#32325d">Whitepapers och concepts</mj-text>
        <mj-text css-class="aligned-center" color="#525f7f" align="center"  font-weight="300">In our work we come accross new ideas and solutions all the time. There are so much innovation just waiting to happen! We cant do it all, not without partners. What we have done is to collect the best thoughts and concepts in one place, so you can read up on the next big thing. Perhaps there is a project there waiting for you? </mj-text>
</mj-column>
</mj-section>
  <mj-section background-color="#f6f9fc">
