<mj-section background-color="#32325d" padding="50px 20px 0 20px" >
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text align="center" font-weight="400" padding="10px 10px 0px 10px" font-size="20px" line-height="20px" text-transform="uppercase" color="#24b47e">A new policy report on FX-risk and ODA</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>


  <mj-section  background-color="#32325d">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text color="#9cdbff" align="center" padding="20px 20px 20px 20px" font-weight="300">In end of May came a new and unique study from the The Expert Group for Aid Studies, EBA. The study, conducted by our director Númi Östlund, analyses the financial risk created by Swedish donor committments in ODA. A main conclusion are that there are significant improvements just waiting to happen. These solutions could provide more and better funding.
</mj-text>
</mj-column>
</mj-section>
  <mj-section background-color="#32325d">
      <mj-column width="100%">
