      <mj-text align="center" font-weight="500" padding="10px 10px 0px 10px" font-size="20px" line-height="20px" text-transform="uppercase" color="#68d4f8">A new site representing a fresh start</mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#525f7f" align="center" padding="20px 20px 20px 20px" font-weight="300">Last week we launched a completely new website. The site not only provide a great new design, but also an update to how we communicate about what we do. The objective has been to get you more by doing less. We have cut down on the clutter, highlighting all the cool things we do. And the same has been implemented througout the entire platform!</mj-text>
          <mj-button href="https://www.aidhedge.org" align="center" background-color="#68d4f8" color="#FFFFFF" border-radius="4px" href="#" inner-padding="10px 17px" padding-bottom="24px" padding-top="20px">VISIT NEW SITE</mj-button>
